data.description: Welcome to your serene retreat nestled within the amenity-rich Lake of the Woods community! Introducing 110 Independence Street, a meticulously crafted 2019 colonial boasting five bedrooms, two full baths, and two half baths sprawled over 3,000 square feet of luxurious living space. Situated on a corner lot ensconced by lush greenery, this home offers unparalleled privacy and tranquility. Immerse yourself in the unparalleled lifestyle offered by Lake of the Woods, boasting a plethora of recreational facilities including a clubhouse, fitness center, equestrian center, lakes and marinas, parks and playgrounds, walking trails, swimming pools, and an 18-hole PGA golf course! Plus, indulge in lakeside relaxation with a pristine beach just a mere half-mile away. Out front, enjoy fresh landscaping as an asphalt driveway leads to the two-car garage.The exterior exudes sophistication with its stone façade, elegant medium gray paneling, a charming white-column draped front porch, and striking blue door/shutters. Entertain guests effortlessly on the expansive wooden deck while enjoying the scenic surroundings, or access the walkout basement exit for seamless outdoor enjoyment. Step inside to discover a neutral and contemporary haven flooded with natural light, complemented by recessed lighting and LVP wood flooring throughout the main level. The layout seamlessly integrates core living spaces including a formal living room (ideal for conversion into an office), a convenient half bath, an inviting family room adorned with a gas fireplace, an eat-in dining area with access to the deck through sliding glass doors, and a well-appointed kitchen boasting granite countertops, a central island in pristine white, stainless steel appliances, and rich dark wood cabinets. Travel to the upper level to find four bedrooms and two full baths, including an oversized primary suite boasting vaulted ceilings, ample windows, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious ensuite bath with a walk-in shower and dual vanity. Three additional bedrooms share a well-appointed full bath complete with a tub/shower combo and a single-vanity sink, all adorned with plush carpeting. Completing this level is a convenient laundry room with washer and dryer!  Descend to the lower level to discover a cozy carpeted retreat featuring a bedroom, a half bath, an open recreation room perfect for entertainment, and a utilities space housing regularly maintained HVAC and hot water heater systems. A sliding glass door provides access to the side yard, perfect for seamless indoor-outdoor living. Strategically located minutes away from historic landmarks such as Chancellorsville and Wilderness Battlefields, as well as numerous golf courses and parks, this home offers a perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Additionally, multiple grocery stores, dining options, and shopping destinations lie within a 15-minute radius, with even more choices along Route 3 within 25 minutes. Centrally positioned within 30 minutes of Culpeper, Orange, and Fredericksburg, this home offers unparalleled accessibility to major urban centers. Experience like-new living, a wealth of amenities, and an enviable location at this Lake of the Woods masterpiece! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make 110 Independence Street your forever home. Schedule your showing today!
